text: == Events == * March 23 - Battle of Uhud (Mohammad looses against the inhabitants from Mecca) * October 27 — Pope Honorius I succeeds Pope Boniface V as the 70th pope. == Births == * Adamnan, abbot of Iona * Empress Wu Zetian of China * Hasan ibn Ali — 2nd Shia Imam and recognised as the 5th Caliph by the Shia * Zhang Jianzhi, Chinese chancellor of the Tang Dynasty (d. 706) == Deaths == * October 25 — Pope Boniface V
